      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a dependable mode of transportation without the price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with some visible scratches, minor paint fading on the roof, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear, and all major electronics are functional, though the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold. Mechanically, it runs well, though it may require routine maintenance soon to keep it in top shape.",
